1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,960
[Story of Yanxi Palace]
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:50,060 --> 00:01:52,259
Drag her away and cane her thirty times.

4
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,240
I'm new to the palace and didn't know
about this spiritual cypress tree.

5
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:59,259
-But I did this for a reason.
-Shut her up.

6
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,730
Let her speak.

7
00:02:03,010 --> 00:02:06,840
I didn't know that
this is the spiritual cypress tree.

8
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:10,759
But I dreamt about...

9
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:12,320
a tree last night.

10
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,680
It told me that
it has been here a long time...

11
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,200
and it is feeling itchy.

12
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,480
So, it asked me to come to the garden...

13
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,079
to give it a scratch.

14
00:02:21,290 --> 00:02:26,070
Yes, I was just giving it
a scratch just now.

15
00:02:26,440 --> 00:02:28,360
What nonsense is this?

16
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:30,760
How could a tree appear in your dream?

17
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:35,120
Since this is a spiritual cypress tree,
of course it could appear in my dream.

18
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:38,260
Your Majesty, I'm telling the truth.

19
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:40,010
I'm not lying.

20
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,730
Forget it. Let's go.

21
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,060
Consider yourself lucky today.

22
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,990
You brat!

23
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,560
Madam.

24
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,440
It hurts.

25
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,200
You also know what pain feels like?

26
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:19,280
You had quite the sharp tongue just now.
You even dared to contradict His Majesty.

27
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,079
Are you tired of living already?

28
00:03:21,850 --> 00:03:23,310
Madam.

29
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:26,090
What kind of tree...

30
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:28,850
is this? Why is it so precious?

31
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:37,360
When His Majesty travelled incognito
back then, it was an extremely hot summer.

32
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,400
All the ministers
were sweating in buckets.

33
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:42,260
His Majesty was the only one
who didn't sweat at all.

34
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,530
Everyone thought that it was strange.

35
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,840
Whenever His Majesty thought about it,

36
00:03:46,890 --> 00:03:50,630
he would roughly remember a giant tree...

37
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:55,010
that accompanied him all the way from
the Forbidden City to give him shade.

38
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:58,280
Everyone said that it was
this spiritual cypress tree.

39
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:01,640
It knew that His Majesty was about
to go travel, so, it went with him...

40
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:04,360
to protect His Majesty on his journey.

41
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:09,070
His Majesty said that to show everyone
that he's the son of heaven...

42
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,440
and is different from everyone.
This cypress tree is just a hoax.

43
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:15,360
-He must be dreaming.
-Watch your mouth.

44
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:17,200
This is just a tree...

45
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:20,660
and we can't even scold it or hit it.
In this Forbidden City,

46
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:23,620
even a tree has better life
than the people here.

47
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:25,880
You are right.

48
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:30,600
In this Forbidden City,
a tree which is favoured by His Majesty...

49
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:33,770
will live better than a woman
who has lost his favour.

50
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:38,300
Look at Noble Lady Yu.
If she can give birth to a son,

51
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,700
she'll be able to turn the table.

52
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:45,180
But for Concubine Yi,
she even lost her life.

53
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,640
Madam.

54
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:54,480
-Let's leave now.
-Why?

55
00:04:54,540 --> 00:04:56,650
His Majesty was distracted by me just now.

56
00:04:56,650 --> 00:04:59,360
If he realises it later,
I will be in big trouble.

57
00:04:59,450 --> 00:05:01,240
-Let's leave.
-Do you think he can't find you?

58
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,760
He won't be able to find me.
All palace maids dress alike.

59
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:07,020
Furthermore, I didn't raise my head
just now. Let's go now.

60
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:11,490
Greetings, mother.

61
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:14,430
Come here. Let me take a look at you.

62
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:23,440
You don't look too good.
Have you been working too hard?

63
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,560
[Empress Dowager]

64
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
Thank you for your concerns.

65
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:28,200
There are too many trivial matters
recently. Nothing to worry about.

66
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,760
In the past, when you woke up
in the morning,

67
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:34,390
you would drink a bowl of
cold sweetened bird nest porridge.

68
00:05:34,840 --> 00:05:38,370
In the evening, you would
drink wine together with your dinner.

69
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:41,760
But lately, you didn't
eat or drink anything at all.

70
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:45,840
Looks like you don't have much appetite.
If you are too exhausted,

71
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:49,000
you can let others handle
certain matters for you.

72
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:52,620
Or else, if you are
doing everything by yourself,

73
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,420
why do you need them for?

74
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:59,710
You are right. But those around me
are too useless.

75
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,730
I will keep them in check.

76
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:07,440
This is the Biluochun tea from Dongting
that Noble Lady Shu gave us.

77
00:06:07,690 --> 00:06:10,060
You love to drink tea.

78
00:06:10,150 --> 00:06:13,010
Take these back with you later.

79
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:19,660
[I dreamt about a tree last night. It told
me that it has been here a long time...]

80
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:23,360
[and it is feeling itchy. So,
it asked me to come to the garden...]

81
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:27,120
[Yes, I was just scratching it just now.]

82
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,880
Your Majesty.

83
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,440
Talking about the Biluochun tea,
there's still another story.

84
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,760
When my father went on a southern tour,

85
00:06:38,850 --> 00:06:41,430
he heard about a tea
with unique fragrance.

86
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:45,280
The natives called it the
"Frightening Fragrance".

87
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:49,610
My father didn't like it.
So, he changed it to Biluochun.

88
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:54,600
It was supposed to be an annual tribute
but when my father became the emperor,

89
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,390
he felt that it was too troublesome.
So, he cancelled it.

90
00:06:57,390 --> 00:07:00,960
If you like it,
I can reinstate the decree.

91
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,840
Don't change the subject.

92
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:05,270
You know what I'm talking about.

93
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,760
Don't you know Noble Lady Shu?

94
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:17,660
Your Majesty, she's the noble lady
who was just selected to enter the palace.

95
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,970
You even conferred a title on her.

96
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:28,150
In the past, you always
praises the empress.

97
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:31,680
She is your rightful wife and
she just gave birth to a son.

98
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:35,520
I couldn't say anything
if you wanted to dote on her.

99
00:07:35,909 --> 00:07:38,760
But she is not in pink health now.

100
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:43,380
You haven't visited the harem for so long.

101
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:47,230
In the past, you said you were
tired of the old faces.

102
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:50,840
But there are many
new ladies in the palace now.

103
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:53,180
Why haven't you visited them?

104
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:57,080
You are right. I understand.

105
00:07:57,200 --> 00:08:00,000
-What do you understand?
- It's so fragrant.

106
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,160
You are changing the subject again.

107
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:04,670
You are already an adult.

108
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:08,610
Stop making me worry.

109
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:14,360
Mother, I still have a lot of reports
to attend to at Yangxin Palace.

110
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,050
I have to leave now.

111
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:19,280
Your Majesty!

112
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,820
Why are you laughing?

113
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:33,480
His Majesty is so funny.

114
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:38,559
He said that he understands.

115
00:08:39,010 --> 00:08:41,919
But I can tell that
he doesn't understand at all.

116
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:46,110
No matter what kind of women
who came into the palace,

117
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:49,710
they'll end up the same.

118
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:55,550
No matter how smart,
beautiful or precious they are,

119
00:08:57,110 --> 00:09:01,430
they'll just end up losing their values...

120
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:07,320
and become someone common.

121
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:38,640
Your Majesty, what are you looking for?

122
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:42,820
Where is that palace maid just now?

123
00:09:43,610 --> 00:09:45,410
Why are you looking for her?

124
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:49,150
I just realised this. Who is she?

125
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:52,900
Why would this spiritual cypress tree
appear in her dream?

126
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:58,040
I can only say that this girl
is too smart and quick-witted.

127
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:02,840
I was too distracted by
the issues of imperial court just now.

128
00:10:03,230 --> 00:10:06,660
I didn't know what to ask.
That's why I let her go.

129
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:10,360
Yes, that girl was full of lies.

130
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:13,080
Furthermore, she sounded so convincing.

131
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:16,050
We have to catch her and kill her.

132
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,020
Your Majesty.

133
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:32,780
Your Majesty, if I did anything wrong,
just ask someone to beat me up.

134
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:37,240
Don't dirty your leg because of me.

135
00:10:38,690 --> 00:10:40,190
Turn around.

136
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:47,520
You are really bold.

137
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:50,880
You reported everything about me
to the Empress Dowager.

138
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:53,760
I know my mistake now.

139
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:56,800
Your Majesty. Madam Liu
came this morning to check on you.

140
00:10:56,800 --> 00:11:00,240
She said that Empress Dowager
is concerned about your health.

141
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,960
So, I could only tell her everything.

142
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:05,420
I know my mistake now.

143
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:09,080
In the future, do not trouble
Empress Dowager with my situation anymore.

144
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,860
I don't want her to worry about me.

145
00:11:10,860 --> 00:11:12,760
Yes, Your Majesty.

146
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,980
Find that palace maid for me.

147
00:11:30,540 --> 00:11:32,010
Your Majesty.

148
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:37,110
Why did you close the door
on Noble Lady Yu?

149
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:41,440
I know that you'll be
furious at me for doing so.

150
00:11:41,880 --> 00:11:46,280
But I still did it for your sake.

151
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:50,190
Tell me. How is it for my sake?

152
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:54,500
I know that you are kind and
will surely help Noble Lady Yu.

153
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:58,520
But there are so many problems in
the palace. Can you handle them all?

154
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:01,200
Those two from Yonghe Palace
are not favoured by His Majesty.

155
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:05,800
Noble Lady Yu is finally pregnant.
But His Majesty still treats her as usual.

156
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:08,680
Why do you want to be involved
in this messy issue?

157
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,150
Why?

158
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:15,000
I am the mother of this nation, role model
of the six palaces, I have to handle this!

159
00:12:15,140 --> 00:12:16,940
What about your own health then?

160
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:19,370
Are you not going to
take care of yourself?

161
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:23,000
Moreover, Noble Consort Gao
is currently at her peak.

162
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:25,450
-You can't control her at all.
-Ming Yu!

163
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,710
-Your Majesty. Calm down.
-Shut up!

164
00:12:28,810 --> 00:12:31,640
Your Majesty, I am concerned about you.

165
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,560
You won't be able to
take care of every problem.

166
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:37,240
We can consider it if we can
topple Noble Consort Gao with it.

167
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:40,520
But we have no chance of winning.
We can't be involved in it.

168
00:12:40,770 --> 00:12:44,210
-Your Majesty.
-What is it that she can't be involved in?

169
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:48,480
Greetings, Your Majesty.

170
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,180
All of you, rise.

171
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,660
What were you all talking about just now?

172
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:57,980
My servants here
are getting more and more lax.

173
00:12:57,980 --> 00:13:00,420
They didn't even announce your arrival.

174
00:13:01,140 --> 00:13:03,600
I'm the one who asked them
not to announce it.

175
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:09,780
I want to see what you are doing.

176
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:14,390
Noble Lady Yu is pregnant.

177
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,510
This is a joyous news in the palace.

178
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:21,270
I want to set up a porridge kitchen
by Shenwu Gate to pray for her child.

179
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:25,760
But they kept saying that
I'm too unwell to do it...

180
00:13:25,920 --> 00:13:27,490
and I shouldn't overexert myself.

181
00:13:27,490 --> 00:13:29,490
So, they are advising me against it.

182
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:33,180
Is that so?

183
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,720
Yes.

184
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:45,540
Other than that,
do you still have other things...

185
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,690
to tell me?

186
00:13:49,190 --> 00:13:52,040
You are busy with
a myriad of state affairs every day.

187
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:53,840
Please take care of your health.

188
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:06,100
Yes.

189
00:14:06,710 --> 00:14:09,290
-Your Majesty.
-I have many state affairs to attend to.

190
00:14:09,290 --> 00:14:11,980
I will attend to them now.
Please rest well.

191
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,780
Farewell, Your Majesty.

192
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,270
Your Majesty.

193
00:14:24,460 --> 00:14:26,720
Why didn't you tell him about it just now?

194
00:14:27,810 --> 00:14:30,140
What's the use of
telling him about it now?

195
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:33,770
Concubine Yi has already passed away.

196
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:38,140
Even if we conduct a further investigation
on that loquat jelly now,

197
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:40,400
it'll not make any difference.

198
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:44,870
My greatest wish now...

199
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:48,210
is for Noble Lady Yu
to pull herself together...

200
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:51,870
and safely deliver her child.

201
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:16,820
Greetings, Noble Consort.

202
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:26,000
What is it? Did His Majesty
ask you to deliver me a gift?

203
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:30,010
Stop.

204
00:15:30,470 --> 00:15:33,330
Please open it in person, Your Highness.

205
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,590
What is it?

206
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,980
Diamond Sutra?

207
00:15:49,280 --> 00:15:52,270
Why did His Majesty give me this?

208
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,430
Your Highness,

209
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:58,490
His Majesty said that you are
too temperamental lately.

210
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:01,880
This sutra is specially given to you.

211
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:06,550
He said that after you copy it once,
you'll be able to calm down.

212
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:09,040
It'll be beneficial for your health.

213
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:17,020
There are 5000 words in this sutra.

214
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:21,660
Your Highness, we've already prepared
brush, ink, papers and ink stone for you.

215
00:16:23,700 --> 00:16:26,120
Leave it here.
I will copy it when I'm free.

216
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:31,120
Your Highness, please forgive me.
His Majesty ordered me to wait here.

217
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:34,190
I have to personally
see you copy the sutra.

218
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,880
And then, I have to take it back for him.

219
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:41,200
What? His Majesty
asked you to monitor me?

220
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,860
Your Highness,
please don't say it that way.

221
00:16:43,890 --> 00:16:46,490
This is His Majesty's
generosity towards you.

222
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:51,420
Don't do it, Your Highness.
This is an imperial gift.

223
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:53,360
You can't throw it.

224
00:16:57,480 --> 00:17:00,180
Fine.

225
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:02,280
I will go and copy it now.

226
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:05,579
Open your eyes and watch me!

227
00:17:06,849 --> 00:17:08,119
Yes, Your Highness.

228
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:11,800
Ji Xiang, look.

229
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,119
What is so good about him?

230
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:21,210
Idiot. Do you think that the guards in
Forbidden City are ordinary people?

231
00:17:21,500 --> 00:17:25,430
This red wall of the Forbidden City
is a dividing line among the guards.

232
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:28,930
What do you mean? I don't understand.

233
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:32,120
You are really dumb.

234
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:35,180
The soldiers outside of this red wall...

235
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:37,780
are of ranking five and below.

236
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,450
But the guards inside this red wall...

237
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:43,320
are royalties from
ranking three and above.

238
00:17:44,610 --> 00:17:46,440
Even royalties will work as guards?

239
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:48,880
Of course. Don't forget.

240
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:53,520
People who are always by His Majesty's
side will surely have a promising career.

241
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:57,720
Hence, when they compete to become a guard
inside the Forbidden City every year,

242
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,420
not only they have to be
from the noble class,

243
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:02,240
they have to be outstanding too.

244
00:18:02,240 --> 00:18:04,680
Or else, they won't stand a chance.

245
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:08,730
I heard that the younger brother of
the empress, Lord Fu Heng, is a guard too.

246
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:10,300
Which one is he?

247
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:12,320
I don't know. I have never seen him too.

248
