493
00:34:52,730 --> 00:34:55,159
For example, the Leather Workshop,
Embroidery House,

494
00:34:55,159 --> 00:34:57,040
Filigree Workshop and Ruyi Workshop.

495
00:34:57,040 --> 00:35:00,000
Call them out. We'll investigate
each and every one of them.

496
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:03,880
This is a decree from His Majesty.
We have to find her.

497
00:35:04,640 --> 00:35:06,360
Lower down this part more.

498
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:10,630
-Look. Here.
-Am I doing it right?

499
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:12,910
Should I make a knot here?

500
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,620
And here.

501
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:25,760
Everyone, get out and form a line.
I'm going to check you one by one.

502
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:29,500
Chief Li. What's going on?

503
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:33,600
Madam Zhang, summon all of
your working maids to come out here.

504
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:35,840
I want to check them one by one.

505
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:40,570
Chief Li, we're rushing to finish
the spring dresses for our mistresses.

506
00:35:40,570 --> 00:35:44,250
If we ask them to come out there,
it'll cause a delay in our work.

507
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:48,260
How about this? If you need anything,
you can just tell me about it.

508
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:51,660
Of course I can't do that.

509
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:55,630
I know that this place is under Eunuch Wu
from the Imperial Household Department.

510
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:58,670
You keep on addressing me
as Chief Li so intimately,

511
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:01,760
are you looking down on me?

512
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:04,640
What are you talking about?
I wouldn't dare do that.

513
00:36:04,640 --> 00:36:08,260
Chief Li, who are you looking for?

514
00:36:08,560 --> 00:36:12,780
A palace maid with a clever mouth
who is full of mischief!

515
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:16,500
If I catch her, I will surely skin her!

516
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,780
Alright. Wait a minute then.

517
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:24,980
Madam, we are in a rush.
We have no time for this.

518
00:36:25,080 --> 00:36:27,920
We can't afford to offend Chief Li.

519
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:34,850
Chief Li, I still have to assist our
two mistresses to try on their dresses.

520
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:36,730
I will be leaving first then.

521
00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:41,200
Move back.

522
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:48,960
Come. Queue up and tell me this.

523
00:36:49,120 --> 00:36:52,390
I was just giving it a scratch.

524
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:55,800
I was just giving it a scratch.

525
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,720
I was just giving it a scratch.

526
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:05,580
I was just giving it a scratch.

527
00:37:06,720 --> 00:37:09,320
I was just giving it a scratch.

528
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,990
I was just giving it a scratch.

529
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:15,020
Why are you laughing?

530
00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:17,060
I'm talking to you!

531
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:21,140
You look like a dummy.

532
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:24,920
That maid is very clever.
You are not her for sure. Step back!

533
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:30,270
Those who are done, don't idle around.

534
00:37:30,270 --> 00:37:33,670
Come with me to deliver
these dresses for our two mistresses.

535
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,640
Chief Li!

536
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,160
Ji Xiang.

537
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:48,300
Such a huge commotion.
Who are you looking for?

538
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,620
Do you need our help?

539
00:37:50,850 --> 00:37:55,240
Although it's an honour, I don't need to
trouble you for trivial matter like this.

540
00:37:55,240 --> 00:37:57,730
"Honour" is too great a word for me.

541
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:03,200
I've invited you over many times
but you always refused me.

542
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:06,680
Noble Lady Shu, you must be joking.
You probably don't know...

543
00:38:06,680 --> 00:38:09,090
His Majesty's temper yet
because you are new here.

544
00:38:09,090 --> 00:38:12,710
If His Majesty finds out that
you invited me,

545
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:17,830
he may think that you're
inquiring information about him.

546
00:38:23,040 --> 00:38:26,290
How can that be?
You are just overthinking it.

547
00:38:26,520 --> 00:38:29,680
I'll be taking my leave then.

548
00:38:40,690 --> 00:38:42,090
Ling Long!

549
00:38:46,320 --> 00:38:49,590
Brat, where did you go?
I couldn't find you anywhere.

550
00:38:49,680 --> 00:38:51,920
-Madam, I...
-You, come over here!

551
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:54,110
I'm talking about you!

552
00:38:55,310 --> 00:38:58,620
Why were you not here just now?

553
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:01,670
You are very suspicious! Say this.

554
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:05,000
I was just giving it a scratch.

555
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:09,450
