556
00:39:10,570 --> 00:39:13,090
Go back. Let's continue.

557
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:19,680
Sister Nalan, are you really
going to track His Majesty?

558
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:22,850
Why are you such a coward?

559
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:27,570
It has been a month since we came in.
But I still haven't seen His Majesty.

560
00:39:28,680 --> 00:39:31,360
Why did we work so hard to pass...

561
00:39:31,540 --> 00:39:33,260
the Consort Selection then?

562
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,920
Did we come here just to bask in the sun?

563
00:39:35,920 --> 00:39:37,520
You can't put it like that.

564
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:40,720
We'll get the chance eventually.

565
00:39:41,160 --> 00:39:43,360
-But if we curry favours like this...
-If you want to be a solider,

566
00:39:43,360 --> 00:39:44,870
aim to be a general.

567
00:39:44,960 --> 00:39:48,120
Since we've come into the palace,
we have to fight to the top.

568
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,860
What's the point of...

569
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:54,220
hiding and cowering
at the corner like a coward?

570
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:56,190
Sister Nalan, lower your voice.

571
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:58,170
What are you afraid of?

572
00:39:58,320 --> 00:40:02,560
I entered the palace to be
a favoured consort, to be above everyone.

573
00:40:02,750 --> 00:40:04,430
Why should I cower in fear?

574
00:40:05,290 --> 00:40:09,270
All of them look so noble and virtuous,
but they are just being pretentious.

575
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:11,480
Let's see if they can avoid
attending to His Majesty forever.

576
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:13,700
Sister Nalan, stop it.

577
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:17,440
All the other sisters in the palace
look quite prim and proper.

578
00:40:17,440 --> 00:40:19,880
You are really naive.

579
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:25,020
I just said a few honest words and
you're already so frightened.

580
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:30,800
Let me tell you, no matter
it's inside or outside the palace,

581
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:34,570
all humans with two legs are all the same.

582
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:39,120
If you see anyone who likes to
flaunt or brag about themselves,

583
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:41,570
don't hesitate. Just spit on them.

584
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:43,660
They are too pretentious!

585
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:46,870
If you want to be a holy person
with a clean heart and mind,

586
00:40:46,870 --> 00:40:50,780
just strangle yourself and go to heaven.

587
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:55,960
Sister Nalan, we still have to greet
Concubine Jia today. Let's go.

588
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:58,430
Wait.

589
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:02,200
Did you hear that?

590
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:05,360
Deliver my dresses back to my palace.

591
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,700
Yes, Your Highness.

592
00:41:07,240 --> 00:41:08,540
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

593
00:41:16,360 --> 00:41:18,460
Look! It's Imperial Guard Fuca!

594
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,820
-Imperial Guard Fuca!
-Jin...

595
00:41:26,250 --> 00:41:28,850
-Imperial Guard Fuca!
-I like him so much!

596
00:41:34,560 --> 00:41:37,240
It's Imperial Guard Fuca!
I saw Imperial Guard Fuca!

597
00:41:37,240 --> 00:41:38,880
-I saw him!
-Imperial Guard Fuca?

598
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,840
Fuca Fu Heng, the brother of the empress.

599
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:44,360
He is well-versed in literature
and military affairs. A royalty!

600
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:46,100
Can we deliver the dresses now?

601
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:49,280
Ying Luo, wait. I need to pee.
Help me with this.

602
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:50,760
Thanks!

603
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:52,520
Jin Xiu!

604
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:27,700
Wei Ying Luo? What are you doing?

605
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:30,200
I should be the one asking that.
